    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document describes an Extensible Provisioning Protocol (EPP) mapping for the provisioning and management of Internet host names stored in a shared central repository.  Specified in XML, the mapping defines EPP command syntax and semantics as applied to host names.  This document obsoletes RFC 4932. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
